title: Main level 2Br w/Granite counters, Appliances, A/C, W/D, Vinyl floors!
posting_body: ['Main level has 2 bedrooms & full bath while 2nd level has master suite with 3/4 bath.', 'Kitchen features granite counters, stainless steel appliances, & vinyl plank flooring.', 'Hardwood floors on main level.', 'Full bathroom has tile flooring & tile surround shower/tub.', 'Carpet on 2nd level.', 'Other conveniences: unfinished basement, garage, & nicely sized, fenced backyard.', 'Appliances included: fridge, stove, dishwasher, washer, dryer, & window a/c unit (no central air).', 'Applicant 18+ must apply, submit credit & background check .', 'Prospective tenant(s) must gross monthly 3x the monthly rent rate, $4,500 - must be verifiable.', 'Security deposit of $1,500 minimum.', 'Tenant pays all utilities.', 'Minimum 550 credit score.', 'Cats & dogs welcome for per pet fee of $250.', '(note: dog subject to review depending on breed).', 'No current or prior evictions or felonies.', 'Property is non-smoking/vaping.', 'Please call me now at:', 'show contact info']
